<v-app
id = 'homepage'>
	<v-main>
		<v-card>
			<v-card-title>homepage</v-card-title>
			<v-tabs>
				<v-tab>乘车公告</v-tab>
				<v-tab>更新日志</v-tab>
				<v-card flat text width="137">
				    <v-select
				        :items="busRouters"
				        v-model="selectBus"
				        solo
				        text
				        flat
				        style="font-size: 14px;"
				    >
				    </v-select>
				</v-card>
				<v-tab-item>
					<v-row
						justify="space-between"
					>
						<v-col 
							fluid
							class = 'column'
						>
							<v-treeview
								dense
								activatable
								color="warning"
								:items="timeSelector">
							</v-treeview>
						</v-col>
						<v-divider vertical></v-divider>
						<v-col>
							<v-card>
								<v-card-title>
									<v-text-field
									v-model="search"
									append-icon="mdi-magnify"
									label="Search"
									single-line
									hide-details
									></v-text-field>
								</v-card-title>
								<v-data-table
									:headers="headers"
									:items="notices"
									:search="search"
								></v-data-table>
							</v-card>
						</v-col>
					</v-row>
				</v-tab-item>
				<v-tab-item>
					
				</v-tab-item>
				<v-tab-item>
					
				</v-tab-item>
			</v-tabs>
		</v-card>
	</v-main>
</v-app>
